Version FINALFIX of deathrun_simpsons!

Changes in FINALFIX:

-This is what you have been waiting for: Homer now have textures! :D
-T:s cannot get guns in easy with CT:S help

It have about 19 traps. 61 spawns for CT and 2 for T. This map also have custom sounds and music + AFK killer + 3 different endings.

I used color pack. I also used couple of textures from ChoGGi:s map de_simpsons_css_v2.

Download and have fun!
